OL,3,CFormer mayor charged with bribery and
OL,4,Cmisconduct in public office
OL,6,FThe former Mayor of Liverpool has been
OL,7,Fcharged with bribery, and misconduct
OL,8,Fin a public office.
OL,10,FJoe Anderson, 67, is among 12 people
OL,11,Fwho have been charged with the
OL,12,Foffences relating to Liverpool City
OL,13,FCouncil contracts between 2010 and
OL,14,F2020.
