OL,3,CFormer mayor charged with bribery and
OL,4,Cmisconduct in public office
OL,6,FFormer Deputy Council Leader Derek
OL,7,FHatton, 77, former Director of
OL,8,FRegeneration Nicholas Kavanagh, 56,
OL,9,Fformer Assistant Director Andrew Barr,
OL,10,F51, have also been charged, alongside
OL,11,FAnderson's son David, 37, Merseyside
OL,12,FPolice said.
OL,14,FThe force added the charges come
OL,15,F"following an extensive investigation
OL,16,F(Operation Aloft) connected to the
OL,17,Fawarding of commercial and business
OL,18,Fcontracts from Liverpool City Council
OL,19,Fbetween 2010 and 2020".
